model.enemies

Class Enemy

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Entity
      • model.enemies.Enemy
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Balloon, Drifblim, GreenPlane, HotAirBalloon, Pterosaur, RedHelicopter

    public class Enemy
extends Entity
    A minimal template for the different Enemies that can be used and drawn in the game.
    Author:
    Ethan Glasberg (glasberg@email.arizona.edu), Jarod Bristol (jarodkylebristol@email.arizona.edu), Alex Gonzalez (aegonzalez793@email.arizona.edu), Patrick Dearborn (pdearborn@email.arizona.edu)

             int speed,

             int gold)
        Custom constructor for an enemy.
        Parameters:
        x - the x coordinate were the enemy will spawn
        y - the y coordinate were the enemy will spawn
        width - the width of the enemy size
        height - the height of the enemy size
        health - the health of the enemy
        speed - the speed of the enemy
        power - how much damage the enemy will do to the player
        gold - the gold gained from killing the enemy
